<view class="container">
    <view class="recommendations">
        <view class="watermark">
            <view>更多知识分享</view>
            <view>小红书@小陈教练</view>
        </view>
        <view class="recommendation-item">
            <text class="title">你的每日饮食建议</text>
        </view>
        <view class="recommendation-item">
            <text class="label">卡路里</text>
            <text class="value">{{recommendations.calories}} 卡</text>
        </view>
        <view class="recommendation-item">
            <text class="label">蛋白质</text>
            <text class="value">{{recommendations.protein}} 克</text>
        </view>
        <view class="recommendation-item">
            <text class="label">脂肪</text>
            <text class="value">{{recommendations.fat}} 克</text>
        </view>
        <view class="recommendation-item">
            <text class="label">碳水化合物</text>
            <text class="value">{{recommendations.carbohydrate}} 克</text>
        </view>
        <view class="disclaimer-text">本计划仅供参考。</view>
    </view>

    <view class="tips">
        <view class="tip-title">对三大营养素没概念？</view>
        <view>移步小红书@小陈教练(带人减脂版)</view>
        <view>有详细的内容讲解及操作流程，助你减脂更快一步。</view>
        <view class="qr-code">
            <image src="{{previewList[0].src}}" data-src="{{previewList[0].src}}" mode="aspectFit" class="qr-image" show-menu-by-longpress="true" bindtap="previewImage"></image>
            <view>{{previewList[0].label}}</view>
        </view>
        <view class="promo">添加好友可获得一整月饮食&健身计划一份</view>
        <view class="qr-code">
            <image src="{{previewList[1].src}}" data-src="{{previewList[1].src}}" mode="aspectFit" class="qr-image" show-menu-by-longpress="true" bindtap="previewImage"></image>
            <view>{{previewList[1].label}}</view>
        </view>
    </view>
</view>
